events.name: EV001 巨大な魚影 自動実行

parameters:
Fisherman Orca: This should be a good spot. Get ready, I'm
going to start throwing the bait now.

Sorceress Sophia: It's quite big... more like a chunk of
meat than bait, isn't it?

Fisherman Orca: ...It's the thigh of a friend who got eaten
by a fish.
Thief Nora: Eh!? Using it as bait is too cruel!

Fisherman Orca: Hahaha, just kidding! But if we leave it
alone, there might be more victims.
Fisherman Orca: So, I'm counting on you.
Clea: Yes, leave it to me.

Fisherman Orca: Well then, I hope it gets caught in one
shot... Here we go!

Sorceress Relm: Could it be... that thing coming towards
us!?

Clea: Everyone, get ready for battle. It seems like this
fresh chunk of meat... prefers living humans as its taste.

Fisherman Orca: We really defeated it! It was a great
decision to rely on you guys for this request!

Clea: Please don't let your guard down... It's still
moving--

Clea: I will go for the rescue! Everyone, please finish off
the fish!
Thief Nora: Yes! Leave it to me!

\CL The giant fish, struck by the flash of the thief Nora,
\CL collapsed and quietly disappeared into the depths of the
lake--.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
